<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/333417-i-listened-to-the-audible-version-of-the">I listened to the Audible version of the first 3 books. After finishing &#39;Truth&#39;, I went to download &#39;Trust&#39; and it wasn&#39;t available. Is there an anticipated release date for this book in an audio format?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_333417'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F21432436-trust">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/333417-i-listened-to-the-audible-version-of-the">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/333417-i-listened-to-the-audible-version-of-the">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

