<span id="freeTextContainer9848852820031108877"><b>*** Warning ! Spoilers everywhere, don&apos;t read this if you hate spoilers!***<br/><br/>I used to loved this series, seriously, I did. I put too much expectation for this one to end good and make me happy and satisfied.<br/>But...</b><br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1380349178ra/703259.gif' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><b>
  <i>
    <blockquote>&quot;That&apos;s not love, that&apos;s dependance&quot;</blockquote>
  </i>
</b><br/><br/>I couldn&apos;t agree more with Cal at so many points. Stephan built dependance to him. Brianna was too, what, most like a pet to him.<br/>He said he loved her, why didn&apos;t feed her and let her be herself?<br/>Or Stephan&apos;s life is all about D/s 24/7? And h</span>
  <span id="freeText9848852820031108877" style="display:none"><b>*** Warning ! Spoilers everywhere, don't read this if you hate spoilers!***<br><br>I used to loved this series, seriously, I did. I put too much expectation for this one to end good and make me happy and satisfied.<br>But...</b><br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1380349178ra/703259.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><b>
